commands.name: az servicebus namespace network-rule-set create
commands.syntax:
az servicebus namespace network-rule-set create --namespace-name
                                                --resource-group
                                                [--default-action {Allow, Deny}]
                                                [--enable-trusted-service-access {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                                [--ip-rules]
                                                [--public-network-access {Disabled, Enabled}]
                                                [--virtual-network-rules]

commands.name: az servicebus namespace network-rule-set list
commands.summary: List list of NetworkRuleSet for a Namespace.

commands.name: az servicebus namespace network-rule-set update
commands.syntax:
az servicebus namespace network-rule-set update [--add]
                                                [--default-action {Allow, Deny}]
                                                [--enable-trusted-service-access {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                                [--force-string {0, 1, f, false, n, no, t, true, y, yes}]
                                                [--ids]
                                                [--ip-rules]
                                                [--namespace-name]
                                                [--public-network-access {Disabled, Enabled}]
                                                [--remove]
                                                [--resource-group]
                                                [--set]
                                                [--subscription]
                                                [--virtual-network-rules]
